pageContext.description: width edge 54mm; width mouth 40.7mm; width loop 9mm; breadth mouth 42.5mm; depth socket 76mm; depth internal ribs 20mm; length external ribs 23.5mm,Three short slightly diverging ribs on either face, quite thick and pronounced; corner angles emphasised by slight rib at edge of narrow facets; discontinuity at mouth on reverse side between two halves; two short internal ribs high on socket; blade tip hollows; casting flash quite protuberant in places; stump of extra flange running round top of mouth; socket end narrow slit? grinding marks observable on edge where patina intact.
pageContext.patina: Little dark green-brown-gold patina; much covered by granular light green surfaces.
pageContext.surface: Edge fairly good and quite sharp in places; light orangey brown soil adhering, esp in sockets.
